    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装：">安装：</h2><p><code>npm install -g nodeppt</code></p>
<h2 id="启动：">启动：</h2><p><code>nodeppt start -d &lt;目录&gt;</code><br><code>nodeppt start -c socket</code><br><code>nodeppt start -d &lt;目录&gt; -p &lt;端口&gt; -H &lt;IP&gt; -c socket</code></p>
<h2 id="手机控制：">手机控制：</h2><p><code>按Q键</code></p>
<h2 id="目录关系">目录关系</h2><p>md同级可以创建img、js、css文件夹来引用静态资源，没有找到使用默认的<code>assets</code>文件夹下的资源   </p>
<h2 id="Theme：">Theme：</h2><p>全局配置：<code>theme: xx 或者 url?theme=xx</code></p>
<ul>
<li>colors</li>
<li>moon</li>
<li>blue</li>
<li>dark</li>
<li>green</li>
<li>light</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="转场动画：">转场动画：</h2><p>全局转场动画：<code>transition: xx</code><br>单页面动画设置：<code>[slide data-transition=&quot;xx&quot;]</code></p>
<ul>
<li>kontext   </li>
<li>vkontext   </li>
<li>circle   </li>
<li>earthquake  </li>
<li>cards   </li>
<li>glue   </li>
<li>stick   </li>
<li>move   </li>
<li>newspaper   </li>
<li>slide   </li>
<li>slide2   </li>
<li>slide3   </li>
<li>horizontal3d   </li>
<li>horizontal   </li>
<li>vertical3d   </li>
<li>zoomin   </li>
<li>zoomout   </li>
<li>pulse   </li>
</ul>
<h2 id="subslide:">subslide:</h2><p>subslide是在一页幻灯片中播放多个子页面   </p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[slide]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[subslide]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="header">子页面1</span><br><span class="line">========</span></span><br><span class="line">子页面2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[/subslide]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="单页背景：">单页背景：</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[slide style="background-image:url('/img/bg1.png')"]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span>      </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="header">## 单页上下布局：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span>markdown</span><br><span class="line">[slide]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="header">## 主页面样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="header">### ----是上下分界线</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="header">上布局</span><br><span class="line">----</span></span><br><span class="line">下布局</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="单条动画：">单条动画：</h2><p>使用方法：列表第一条加上 ` {:&amp;.动画类型}``（注意空格）</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>单条动画 &#123;:&amp;.zoomIn&#125;   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>单条动画</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>单条动画</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>单条动画：    </p>
<ul>
<li>moveIn</li>
<li>fadeIn</li>
<li>bounceIn</li>
<li>rollIn</li>
<li>zoomIn</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="对齐">对齐</h2><p>使用方法：加上 {:&amp;.flexbox.vleft}</p>
<h2 id="标题">标题</h2><p>封面使用h1，内部使用h2 </p>
